co-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 24, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104quf1665702550125.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quf1665702550125.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quf1665702550125.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"quf1665702550125\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Application Shell\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"quf1665702550125__application_shell_311796\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An Application Shell is a Main Development Object that defines the main executable component of an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quf1665702550125__topic_d63542e1_d63543e1_d63544e1_d63545e1_d63546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1093113e53\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"quf1665702550125__image_vmp_w1n_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/shell.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">aps</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ApplicationName</var>.aps</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">aps:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ApplicationName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quf1665702550125__topic_d63547e1_d63548e1_d63549e1_d63550e1_d63551e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1093113e265\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quf1665702550125__p_d95273e1_d95274e1_d95275e1\">Application Shell specializes Main Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37547e1_d37548e1_d37549e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quf1665702550125__p_d95276e1_d95277e1_d95278e1\">It contains no development objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quf1665702550125__topic_d63552e1_d63553e1_d63554e1_d63555e1_d63556e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1093113e283\">\n                     \n Properties\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Common</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quf1665702550125__p_d95282e1_d95283e1_d95284e1\">The following properties are common to several types\n            of application shell:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37550e1_d37551e1_d37552e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rex1665702714530.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rex1665702714530.html\" title=\"Determines the type of application that the startup shell executes. The type of shell determines the properties and triggers that you can define.\">Shell Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37553e1_d37554e1_d37555e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyl1665702688770.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyl1665702688770.html\" title=\"Specifies the library containing the global objects used by the component or application shell. If no library is specified, the library defined for the application shell is used. Otherwise, SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used as the default.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37556e1_d37557e1_d37558e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vjc1665702714625.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vjc1665702714625.html\" title=\"This property defines an associative list of application shell properties. The available properties depend on the type of application shell.\">Window/App</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37559e1_d37560e1_d37561e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1665702689407.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1665702689407.html\" title=\"Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed.\">Title</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37562e1_d37563e1_d37564e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"glg1665702714695.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/glg1665702714695.html\" title=\"Name of the menu bar initially displayed for the current form or application shell.\">Menu Bar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37565e1_d37566e1_d37567e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nnt1665702586853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nnt1665702586853.html\" title=\"Name of the pop-up menu object to display when the user clicks the mouse button in this component, entity, or field.\">Pop-up Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37568e1_d37569e1_d37570e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtq1665702714794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtq1665702714794.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the panel that is displayed with the form or application shell at runtime.\">Panel</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37571e1_d37572e1_d37573e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oat1665702714863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oat1665702714863.html\" title=\"Specifies a panel that is available for the duration of the application session, even if a panel has been specified for the current component, or a toolbar definition exists.\">Session Panel</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37574e1_d37575e1_d37576e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"txw1665702714934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txw1665702714934.html\" title=\"Position of the panel for a form or application shell when displayed at runtime.\">Panel Position</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\">Windows Application Shells</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quf1665702550125__p_d95288e1_d95289e1_d95290e1\">The following properties apply to the application window and other behavior:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Window and Other Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Property Name</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hse1665702715007.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hse1665702715007.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu in the title bar.\">Setup</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Setup</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kno1665702715076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665702715076.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False.\">Caption</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Caption</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjr1676877187333.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjr1676877187333.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the window can be resized at runtime.\">Resizable (CanResize)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">CanResize</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cwr1665702715216.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwr1665702715216.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the user can minimize the form or application window at run time, and enables the Minimize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Iconize (CanIconize)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">CanIconize</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qkn1665702715286.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkn1665702715286.html\" title=\"Determines whether the user can maximize and restore the size of the form or application window using the Maximize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Maximize</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">CanZoom</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dvg1665702715374.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dvg1665702715374.html\" title=\"Determines whether the application window is treated as a Microsoft Windows dialog box, so the window is not resizable.\">Dialog</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dialog</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecw1665702715443.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.\">System Menu (SysMenu)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">SysMenu</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fym1665702715516.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fym1665702715516.html\" title=\"Window property of an application shell that determines how the application window is closed.\">Close (CanClose) [APS]</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">CanClose</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gqy1665702715592.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqy1665702715592.html\" title=\"Determines whether all forms that are run in the application shell are maximized.\">Maximized Forms</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MaximizedForms</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">BackColor</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wjh1665702607394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wjh1665702607394.html\" title=\"The MessageLine property determines whether the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display non-obtrusive messages to the user.\">Message Line</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MessageLine</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Image Properties</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following properties apply to a background image, if specified. Default values for\n            these properties can be set using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Shell</span> setting in the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Image Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Property Name</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">BackImage</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">ForeColor</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">HAlign</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">VAlign</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Hscale</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">VScale</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"quf1665702550125__table_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">PreserveAspect</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quf1665702550125__topic_d63577e1_d63578e1_d63579e1_d63580e1_d63581e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1093113e906\"> Triggers </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37577e1_d37578e1_d37579e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jcj1665702550017.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcj1665702550017.html\" title=\"System trigger that starts the application environment and controls the interaction of the application with the component manager.\">trigger apStart</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37580e1_d37581e1_d37582e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uwh1665702683119.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uwh1665702683119.html\" title=\"System trigger for handling any global pre-processing, such as verifying the environment or user permissions.\">trigger preRequest</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37583e1_d37584e1_d37585e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bar1665702683338.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bar1665702683338.html\" title=\"System trigger for handling any global post processing, such as closing a database or writing a log file.\">trigger postRequest</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37586e1_d37587e1_d37588e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37589e1_d37590e1_d37591e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sux1665703129629.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sux1665703129629.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a request for a pulldown menu in a desktop application.\">trigger pullDown</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37592e1_d37593e1_d37594e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"niy1665702606431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/niy1665702606431.html\" title=\"Trigger for responding to user-defined key sequences as defined in the Keyboard Translation Table (KTT) or defined in the usys.ini section named as userkeys.\">trigger userKey</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37595e1_d37596e1_d37597e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xye1665702608643.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xye1665702608643.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request for a menu in a desktop application.\">trigger menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quf1665702550125__li_d37598e1_d37599e1_d37600e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ppz1665702665163.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ppz1665702665163.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger that defines the application-wide actions in response to the ^SWITCH_KEY action, such as loading a new keyboard translation table.\">trigger keyboardSwitch</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohj1705472401504.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Application Shells</a><p>An application shell is a module used to initialize and run an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615513\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615513\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Application Shell Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 24, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Application Shell An Application Shell is a Main Development Object that defines the main executable component of an application (Windows or character-based) or application server. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: aps Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Property , Code Container Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: ApplicationName .aps URI format: aps: ApplicationName Specialization Application Shell specializes Main Development Object in the following ways: It contains no development objects. Properties Common The following properties are common to several types of application shell: Shell Type Library Window/App Title Menu Bar Pop-up Menu Panel Session Panel Panel Position Windows Application Shells The following properties apply to the application window and other behavior: Table 1. Window and Other Properties Property Technical Property Name Setup Setup Caption Caption Resizable (CanResize) CanResize Iconize (CanIconize) CanIconize Maximize CanZoom Dialog Dialog System Menu (SysMenu) SysMenu Close (CanClose) [APS] CanClose Maximized Forms MaximizedForms Background Color (BackColor) BackColor Message Line MessageLine Image Properties The following properties apply to a background image, if specified. Default values for these properties can be set using the Shell setting in the usys.ini file. Table 2. Image Properties Property Technical Property Name Background Image (BackImage) BackImage Foreground Color (ForeColor) ForeColor Horizontal Alignment (Halign) HAlign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) VAlign Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Hscale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) VScale Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) PreserveAspect Triggers trigger apStart trigger preRequest trigger postRequest trigger receiveMessage trigger pullDown trigger userKey trigger menu trigger keyboardSwitch Related Links Application Shells An application shell is a module used to initialize and run an application (Windows or character-based) or application server. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}